## :pencil2: Usage

To use any framework availible in this repo add cocoapods dependency in podfile.

**Example:**
```ruby
pod 'ZappCore', :git => 'https://github.com/applicaster/AppleApplicasterFrameworks.git', :tag => '2020.15.0.20-1-6'
```
